            Dahua's traffic solutions are deployed across Asia, MENA, Europe, Latin America, Brazil and beyond, helping customers solve complex traffic management challenges with customized solutions.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed animate-slide-up-delayed">
